file.name: users.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info: {}
paths:
    /users/{id}/extended:
        patch:
            summary: Update a user's extended fields.
            tags:
                - Users
            parameters:
                - description: The user ID.
                  in: path
                  name: id
                  required: true
                  schema:
                      type: integer
            requestBody:
                content:
                    application/json:
                        schema:
                            $ref: "#/components/schemas/ExtendedUserFields"
                required: true
            responses:
                "200":
                    content:
                        "application/json":
                            schema:
                                $ref: "#/components/schemas/ExtendedUserFields"
                    description: Success
components:
    schemas:
        ExtendedUserFields:
            type: object
            description: The user's profile extender fields.
